{"descriptions":[{"id":1170,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe future is formed by placing after the verb the particles: \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་རེད་\u003c/span\u003e (assertive) or \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་ཡིན་\u003c/span\u003e (intentional egophoric). These are composed by adding the essential copula \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརེད་\u003c/span\u003e or \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡིན་\u003c/span\u003e to the suffix\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003e གི་\u003c/span\u003e. In written Tibetan,\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003e གི་\u003c/span\u003e has several possible variants according to the final consonant of the preceding syllable. The pattern of these variants is the same as in the case of the genitive, except for vowels and the letter\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003e འ་\u003c/span\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་\u003c/span\u003e is used after vowels and \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eའ་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་\u003c/span\u003e,\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003e ང་\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp; \u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཀྱི་ \u003c/span\u003eis used after \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eད་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eབ་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eས་\u003c/span\u003e, and the second crypted suffix \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eད་\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u0026nbsp; \u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགྱི་\u003c/span\u003e is used after \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eན་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eམ་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eར་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eལ་\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp; \u003c/li\u003e \u003c/ul\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eIn Spoken Tibetan, the suffix is pronounced gi in all cases.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe intentional form \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་ཡིན་\u003c/span\u003e may be used only with volitional verbs in the first person. In interrogative sentences, the egophoric form \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་ཡིན་ \u003c/span\u003eis replaced by\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003e གས་ \u003c/span\u003eif the statement contains no interrogative pronoun, and by \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་\u003c/span\u003e otherwise.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe different forms are given in the following table:\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTable: The Future Auxiliaries\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003ctable border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"\u003e \u003ctbody\u003e \u003ctr\u003e \u003ctd width=\"113\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eAffirmative\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"136\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eInterrogative\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e(without pronoun)\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"113\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eInterrogative\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e(with pronoun)\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"113\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eNegative\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"113\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eNegative Interrogative\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003c/tr\u003e \u003ctr\u003e \u003ctd width=\"113\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་ཡིན་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"136\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་ཡིན་པས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eགས་\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"113\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"113\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་མིན་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"113\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་མིན་པས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003c/tr\u003e \u003ctr\u003e \u003ctd width=\"113\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་རེད་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"136\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་རེད་པས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"113\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་རེད་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"113\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་མ་རེད་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"113\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་མ་རེད་པས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003c/tr\u003e \u003c/tbody\u003e \u003c/table\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eSome basic example sentences:\u003c/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eསང་ཉིན་མོག་མོག་བཟོ་གི་ཡིན།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Tomorrow I shall make momos.\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eསང་ཉིན་མོག་མོག་བཟོ་གི་རེད།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Tomorrow he/she will make momos.\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e \u003c/ul\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":true,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:14:03 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:14:03 UTC","authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}]}]}